post_text: Governor JB Pritizker has issued a "stay-at-home" order that will help prevent the spread of COVID-19. This order will stay in affect through April 7th. During this time PRSD 143.5 District Office and School Offices will be closed. Gordon and Kellar School will remain open Monday - Friday, 9am - 12noon for 'grab and go' breakfast and lunch pick up for district students. As news and updates have the possibility of changing continuously, we will give updates as it relates to our school district. We hope that everyone remains healthy and safe during this very difficult time.
